OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FApart from some early
OL,6,Fbrightness today will be a rather
OL,7,Fcloudy day with outbreaks of rain. The
OL,8,Frain likely to become heavier and more
OL,9,Fpersistent later this afternoon.
OL,10,FBreezy, especially near Irish Sea
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA wet evening and night to
OL,14,Fcome with the rain heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent at times, especially over
OL,16,Fthe hills. Windy initially, although
OL,17,Feasing later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
