OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA wet start to the day,
OL,6,Fespecially in the south. Rain will
OL,7,Fclear to the east by the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith a mix of sunny spells and a few
OL,9,Fshowers following.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FStaying unsettled with a mixture of
OL,13,Fsunshine and showers on Tuesday and
OL,14,FWednesday, before turning wet and
OL,15,Fwindy on Thursday. Temperatures around
OL,16,For a little below average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
